python3-linkrot (5.2.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release 5.2.2
  * Added retraction checking functionality
  * Check DOIs against retraction databases to identify potentially retracted papers
  * Multiple detection methods: CrossRef API and metadata analysis
  * Rate limiting and caching for respectful API usage
  * Comprehensive error handling
  * New CLI option: -r, --check-retractions
  * JSON output includes retraction check results
  * Added requests dependency for API communications
  * Updated pyproject.toml with new dependency
  * Enhanced DOI extraction and validation
  * Added comprehensive test suite for retraction functionality
  * Added example usage demonstrations

